article_headline: Senior Meg Mitchell gives Cal Poly needed emotional spark for success
article_text: Pomona, the Mustangs trailed by as much as 22 points in the first half before finally losing, 112-101. The Broncos are led by senior Chancellor McCobb, a forward who has averaged close to 19 points a game. Poly also hosts Cal State Los Angeles on Saturday at 8 p.m.
